    <desc>Choose between dynamic workspaces that automatically adjust
    based on usage or a fixed number of workspaces. Also, configure how
    workspaces appear across multiple monitors.</desc>
 
    <include href="legal.xml" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2001/XInclude"/>
